Class AbstractTransientStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.store.AbstractTransientStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OwnedTransientStore, SynchronizedTransientStore

    public abstract class AbstractTransientStore
extends Object
implements TransientStore
    A abstract TransientStore that uses collections to store data in memory.
